<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='994011' id='t-994011'>My friend Adam Curtis says</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='996782' id='t-996782'>that maybe the Internet is like
a John Carpenter movie from the 1980s,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1000614' id='t-1000614'>when eventually everyone
