<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1003679' id='t-1003679'>and shooting each other,
and then eventually everybody</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1006233' id='t-1006233'>would flee to somewhere safer,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1008253' id='t-1008253'>and I'm starting to think of that
