</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
17:03
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1012177' id='t-1012177'>BG: Jon, thank you.
JR: Thank you, Bruno.</span>
</span>
</p>
